tensorflow/contrib/makefile/compile_linux_protobuf.sh

body:
Sorry you're hitting problems! This looks like a mismatch between the protobuf version that's installed in your /usr/local system folders, and the one that was used to create the .pb.cc/.h files. Can you try running this command to build a local copy of the libs?

```
tensorflow/contrib/makefile/compile_linux_protobuf.sh
```
